Package marsbars

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Controller
    Responsible for all the common methods shared between each device/sensor controllers.
    EnvironmentController
    Responsible for the Greenhouse Environment start parameters and the external effects on the Greenhouse.
    EnvironmentModel
    Model responsible for calculations that are required to simulate the effect of external effects on the greenhouse.
    EnvironmentView
    GUI elements for the Greenhouse environment external effects panel
    GreenhouseSimulator
    Main class that brings it all toghether and contains the simulation control functions.
    GUI
    This class combines all the controller/sensor panel GUIs and adds GUI elements for file control
    HumidityController
    Controller responsible for the Humidity Controller/Sensor functionality.
    HumidityModel
    Model responsible for calculations that are required for the humidity sensor and humidifier control.
    HumidityView
    GUI elements for the Greenhouse humidity control panel
    MoistureController
    Controller responsible for the Soil Moisture Controller/Sensor functionality.
    MoistureModel
    Model responsible for calculations that are required for the soil moisture sensor and sprinkler control.
    MoistureView
    GUI elements for the Greenhouse soil moisture control panel
    RangeSlider
    An extension of JSlider to select a range of values using two thumb controls.
    TemperatureController
    Controller responsible for the Temperature Controller/Sensor functionality.
    TemperatureModel
    Model responsible for calculations that are required for the temperature sensor and furnace and air conditioner control.
    TemperatureView
    GUI elements for the Greenhouse temperature control panel
